---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="Real Estate Accounting — CA Accounting | Investors, Developers, Brokers"
  description="Specialty accounting for real estate: investors, developers, property managers, brokers, and agents. Depreciation strategies, 1031 exchanges, multi-property bookkeeping, and K-1 handling."
>
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">Industries · Real Estate</p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl font-serif text-navy leading-tight mb-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          The accounting work behind the portfolio.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          We work with property managers, developers, investors, brokers, and agents — the people whose financials live across LLCs, K-1s, depreciation schedules, and sometimes a 1031 exchange clock that nobody warned them about. Our job is to keep all of it organized and tax-efficient.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-12 mb-16">
        <div class="lg:col-span-1 fade-in">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">What we handle</h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Real estate is one of the most tax-advantaged asset classes — and one of the easiest to mishandle. Our work is organized around the structures and strategies that make a difference.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Depreciation strategies</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Cost segregation studies, bonus depreciation, and accelerated depreciation modeling to capture deductions correctly the first time.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">1031 exchanges</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Exchange planning, identification-period support, and reporting — coordinating with your QI to keep the exchange clean.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Multi-property bookkeeping</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Per-property P&Ls, allocated expense tracking, and consolidated portfolio reporting across LLCs.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">K-1 preparation & review</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Partnership and LLC K-1 issuance for syndicates, joint ventures, and family-held holdings.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Passive activity rules</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Real estate professional status analysis, grouping elections, and passive loss tracking across properties.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-navy mb-2">Entity structuring</h3>
              <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm leading-relaxed">Single-member and multi-member LLCs, holding company structures, and basis tracking for distributions and refinances.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Who we work with</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
            From a first rental to a hundred-door portfolio.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-cream/80 text-base leading-relaxed">
            Solo investors with a few rentals, syndicators raising capital, developers building from the ground up, and the brokers and agents serving them. Every engagement is structured around how the work actually flows in your business.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-cream/70 text-sm fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Investors & landlords</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Developers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Property managers</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Brokers & agents</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Syndicators & GPs</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Family holding entities</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Short-term rental operators</div>
          <div class="border border-cream/10 rounded p-4">Commercial owners</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Have a property or a portfolio that needs cleaner books?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-10">
          Schedule a free consultation. We'll look at your current structure and tell you what we'd do differently — and whether it's worth the effort.
        </p>
        <a
          href="/contact"
          class="btn-modern inline-block bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-10 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover transition-colors"
        >
          Schedule a Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
